PrecisAmendment to the EARLY DEPARTURE INCENTIVE PROGRAM ORDER whereby Transport Canada employees in the Safety and Security Unit at John G. Diefenbaker Airport in Saskatoon who have not received an early departure incentive offer before March 26, 1996, will no longer be eligible for same.
